OL,6,FThe widow and daughter of murdered MP
OL,7,FSir David Amess are set to meet with
OL,8,Fthe Home Secretary to push for
OL,9,F"answers" over missed opportunities in
OL,10,Fthe lead-up to his death.
OL,12,FLady Julia Amess and Katie Amess are
OL,13,Fset for talks with Shabana Mahmood on
OL,14,FWednesday, with Sir David's daughter
OL,15,Fdescribing the meeting as one about
OL,16,F"accountability, transparency, and
OL,17,Flearning lessons properly".
