OL,6,FKatie Amess has made repeated calls
OL,7,Ffor a public inquiry into her father's
OL,8,Fmurder, saying it is the only way to
OL,9,Fachieve "real accountability".
OL,11,FFormer home secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,12,Fpreviously wrote to Sir David's family
OL,13,Fto reject their calls for an inquiry,
OL,14,Fwhich Lady Amess and Katie branded
OL,15,F"totally unacceptable" and "insulting".
