OL,6,FSir David was stabbed to death at his
OL,7,Fconstituency surgery in Essex in 2021
OL,8,Fby so-called Islamic State fanatic Ali
OL,9,FHarbi Ali, who was sentenced to a
OL,10,Fwhole-life order for the murder the
OL,11,Ffollowing year.
OL,13,FAli had been referred to Prevent seven
OL,14,Fyears before he killed the veteran MP,
OL,15,Fbut his case was closed in 2016.
