OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the meeting, Katie
OL,7,Fsaid in a statement: "Tomorrow I will
OL,8,Fbe meeting the Home Secretary to
OL,9,Fdiscuss the circumstances surrounding
OL,10,Fthe murder of my father, Sir David
OL,11,FAmess.
OL,13,F"I am looking forward to this meeting
OL,14,Fand to engaging constructively with
OL,15,Fthe Government.
