OL,3,CMurdered MP's family to meet Home
OL,4,CSecretary to push for 'answers'
OL,6,F"The failures that led to his death
OL,7,Fwere not abstract or theoretical, they
OL,8,Fwere real, and they had devastating
OL,9,Fconsequences for our family."
OL,11,FShe continued: "This meeting is about
OL,12,Faccountability, transparency, and
OL,13,Flearning lessons properly.
OL,15,F"It is about ensuring that no other
OL,16,Ffamily has to endure what we have
OL,17,Fendured because warnings were missed,
OL,18,Frisks were underestimated, or
OL,19,Fopportunities to intervene were not
OL,20,Ftaken.
