OL,4,CSecretary to push for 'answers'
OL,6,F"We remain committed to working with
OL,7,Fthe Government to get the answers we
OL,8,Fneed and deserve.
OL,10,F"But we are equally clear that this
OL,11,Fprocess must be rigorous, independent,
OL,12,Fand capable of addressing the very
OL,13,Fobvious failures that occurred.
OL,15,F"Anything less would fall short of
OL,16,Fjustice for my father and for the
OL,17,Fpublic he served so faithfully."
